//
//  StarCatalog.swift
//  AstroSky
//
//  Embedded catalog of bright stars: every star of the major constellation
//  figures plus the brightest named stars of both hemispheres.
//
//  Positions are J2000.0 (RA in hours, Dec in degrees), magnitudes are
//  apparent visual magnitudes, colors are B−V indices, distances are
//  light-years. Sources: Yale Bright Star Catalogue / Hipparcos values.
//
//  For a deeper sky (thousands of stars) drop the HYG database CSV into the
//  app bundle — see HYGCatalogLoader.
//

